project_descr: Inventory, Evaluation and Monitoring of Botanical Diversity in Southern Africa

outputs.output_descr: Increased capacity of professional Southern African plant taxonomists and plant diversity specialists, formal collaborating Southern African Botanical Diversity Network, a functional electronic information system on region's plant diversity, increased knowledge of regional plant taxonomic expertise and infrastructure, an increased capacity for plant diversity evaluations and monitoring within the region and increased capcity in Southern Africa to initiate a regional botanical gardens conservation strategy.
